    <!--
This is a third series after Easy Photomap, Easy diary.
Easy Password is an application that helps you manage passwords used for login, document security, door lock, lock, credit card, account management, etc. by using one pattern lock set by the user.
All passwords managed by Easy Password are encrypted and stored using the lock pattern set by the user.

Do not write your password on your notepad dangerously.
Do not set multiple passwords the same for easier remembering.
From now on, you can safely manage your password with a single lock pattern using Easy Password.

Easy Password does not collect or store your personal information.
The password management information registered by the user is stored in the user's device and is not transmitted to other server.
When using the Google Drive Backup feature, the Realm Backup File is stored in the drive of the user account, but it is stored in the user's personal account and can not be collected or stored externally.
Also, since the password information is AES password, it can not be decrypted without the lock pattern information set by the user.

<b>[Support Feature]</b>
<b><font color="#185A32">01. Application lock with pattern</font></b>
<b><font color="#185A32">02. Encryption and decryption with AES of passwords to be managed using lock pattern</font></b>
<b><font color="#185A32">03. Backup and recovery of management list using Google Drive</font></b>
